| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2375 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7441b1a1-ce5c-55ff-82fa-d5c81f0de169"
